<li id="cite_note-24"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-24">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Years later, Smith would state that "the Book of Mormon was the most correct of any book on earth, and the keystone of our religion <a href="/wiki/Mormonism" title="Mormonism">Mormonism</a>, and a man would get nearer to God by abiding by its precepts, than by any other book."</span>
