</li>
<li id="cite_note-27"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-27">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">This is widely viewed by secular scholars as an opposition to <a href="/wiki/Freemasonry" title="Freemasonry">Freemasonry</a>, although years later Smith would become a Freemason himself.</span>
